result.longName: Changzhou Architectural Research Institute Group Co.,Ltd

assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Changzhou Architectural Research Institute Group Co.,Ltd provides architectural research and technological services in China. It offers detection and identification services, such as project quality inspection, professional non-destructive testing, traffic inspection, and environmental testing; special construction, foundation and foundation engineering, and building maintenance services; and consulting and design services comprising geotechnical engineering design and consultation, as well as green building technical and special technical plan consultation. The company also provides certified product services; floor and ceramic tile anti-skid projects in public areas; non-knock floor tiles repair methods for leaks in toilets and bathrooms; sunlight rooms, glass rooms, and other reflective insulation coatings; and external wall waterproof materials. In addition, it offers green building materials consisting of concrete admixtures, building energy-saving insulation systems, and high-speed rail new materials; dry mortar-ready-mixed mortars, matching mortar for new wall materials, special mortars, and colored mortars; functional materials, such as reinforcement, repair, home improvement, etc.; environment-friendly wear-resistant floor systems; concrete rigid self-waterproof systems; and GMT impact-resistant mortars. The company was founded in 1959 and is headquartered in Changzhou, China.
